        </h1>
        <div class="home__site-container">
            <div class="home__heading">
                <div class="home__title">
                    Разработка на 1С-Битрикс + Битрикс24: запускаем,<br>
                    развиваем,<br>
                    <span class="home__mobile-word">поддерживаем</span>
                    <div class="home__desktop-word-wrapper">

                        <div class="home__desktop-word">под(</div>
                        <ul class="home__words-list home__words-slogan">
                            <li>Мы —</li>
                            <li>интеллектуальный</li>
                            <li>лифт, построенный</li>
                            <li>из кода, дизайна</li>
                            <li>и стратегии. С нами</li>
                            <li>это работает</li>
                            <li>стабильно. Вы</li>
                            <li>управляете бизнесом,</li>
                            <li>мы — всей</li>
                            <li>технической частью</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="home__desktop-word">)держиваем</div>
                    </div>
                </h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="simple-section section" data-section="yellow">
    <div class="simple-section__site-container">
        <div class="simple-section__body">
            <h2 class="simple-section__title">
                Работаем с&nbsp;2012 года<br> и&nbsp;помогаем<br> интернет-магазинам&nbsp;расти
            </h2>

            <ul class="simple-section__list">
                <li class="simple-section__item">
                    разрабатываем на 1С-битрикс
                </li>
                <li class="simple-section__item">
                    приводим клиентов с SEO
                </li>
                <li class="simple-section__item">
                    поддерживаем и дорабатываем проекты
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="video-section section">
    <div class="video-section__wrapper">
        <video id="player" playsinline controls data-poster="./img/formats/poster.png">
            <source src="./img/video/video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            <source src=./img/video.webm" type="video/webm" />
        </video>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="advantages-section section">
    <div class="advantages-section__site-container">
        <div class="advantages-section__body">
            <div class="advantages-section__heading home__heading">
                <div class="home__title home__title--smaller">
                    Почему интернет-<br class="home__title-desktop-transfer">
                    <span class="home__margin-desktop-word">магазины</span>
                    <span class="home__mobile-word">выбирают нас?</span>
                    <div class="home__desktop-word-wrapper">

                        <div class="home__desktop-word">вы(</div>
                        <ul class="home__words-list home__advantages">
                            <li class="home__advantage advantage">
                                <div class="advantage__counter">
                                    первое
                                </div>
                                <p class="advantage__text">
                                    Комплексный подход: разработка, поддержка, SEO
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="home__advantage advantage">
                                <div class="advantage__counter">
                                    второе
                                </div>
                                <p class="advantage__text">
                                    Глубокая экспертиза в 1С-Битрикс.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="home__advantage advantage">
                                <div class="advantage__counter">
                                    третье
                                </div>
                                <p class="advantage__text">
                                    Быстрое реагирование: критические задачи решаем за 5-15 минут
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="home__advantage advantage">
                                <div class="advantage__counter">
                                    четвертое
                                </div>
                                <p class="advantage__text">
                                    Готовы работать и&nbsp;в&nbsp;нерабочее время
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="home__advantage advantage">
                                <div class="advantage__counter">
                                    пятое
                                </div>
                                <p class="advantage__text">
                                    Честное ценообразование: без&nbsp;«сгорающих» часов и&nbsp;скрытых платежей
                                </p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="home__desktop-word">)бирают нас?</div>
                    </div>
                </h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>




<section class="feedback-section section">
    <div class="feedback-section__site-container">
        <form action="" class="feedback-section__form" data-need-validation>
            <h2 class="feedback-section__title">
                Давайте обсудим&nbsp;Ваш проект!
            </h2>

            <div class="feedback-section__column">
                <div class="feedback-section__row feedback-section__row--left">
                    <div class="feedback-section__input-box input-box input-box--for-dark">
                        <input type="text" name="feedback-name" id="feedback-name-id" required placeholder="Ваше имя" data-parsley-required="">
                        <label for="feedback-name-id" class="input-box__label">Ваше имя</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feedback-section__row feedback-section__row--left">
                    <div class="feedback-section__input-box input-box input-box--for-dark">
                        <input type="tel" name="feedback-phone" id="feedback-phone-id" required placeholder="Номер телефона" data-parsley-phone="">
                        <label for="feedback-phone-id" class="input-box__label">Номер телефона</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feedback-section__row feedback-section__row--left">
                    <div class="feedback-section__input-box input-box input-box--for-dark">
                        <input type="text" name="feedback-company" id="feedback-company-id" required placeholder="Компания" data-parsley-required="">
                        <label for="feedback-company-id" class="input-box__label">Компания</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feedback-section__row feedback-section__row--right">
                    <div class="feedback-section__input-box input-box input-box--for-dark">
                        <textarea rows="1" name="feedback-comment" id="feedback-comment-id"  placeholder="Какие стоят задачи?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feedback-section__row feedback-section__row--right">
                    <div class="feedback-section__types">
                        <span class="feedback-section__types-title">
                            Тип работ:
                        </span>
                        <ul class="feedback-section__types-list">
                            <li>
                                <label class="feedback-section__type nameplate">
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="nameplate-type" hidden id="nameplate-type-01" value="dev">
                                    разработка
                                </label>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <label class="feedback-section__type nameplate">
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="nameplate-type"hidden  id="nameplate-type-02" value="dev-2">
                                    развитие
                                </label>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <label class="feedback-section__type nameplate">
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="nameplate-type" hidden id="nameplate-type-03" value="support">
                                    тех.поддержка
                                </label>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <label class="feedback-section__type nameplate">
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="nameplate-type"hidden  id="nameplate-type-04" value="seo">
                                    SEO
                                </label>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <label class="feedback-section__type nameplate">
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="nameplate-type"hidden  id="nameplate-type-05" value="bitrix">
                                    Битрикс24
                                </label>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feedback-section__row feedback-section__row--right feedback-section__controls">
                    <button type="submit" class="feedback-section__submit button button--white">
                        Оставить заявку
                    </button>

                    <div class="feedback-section__agreement">
                        <label class="feedback-section__agreement-checkbox checkbox">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="feedback-agreement" id="agreement-id" hidden required>
                            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-border">
                                <use xlink:href="#border"></use>
                            </svg>
                            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-thick">
                                <use xlink:href="#thick"></use>
                            </svg>
                        </label>
                        <p class="feedback-section__agreement-text">
                            Даю свое согласие на&nbsp;
                            <a href="#" target="_blank">обработку персональных данных</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- <div class="feedback-section__captcha"></div> -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>

{{/content}}
{{/extend}}
